snippet.textDisplay:
When you mentioned Cinnabon I was like.. hold on, I recognise those?! Turns out when I got addicted to watching those ‘eating 10k calories in 24hr’ challenge videos (remember them?! Haha!) the American youtubers used to buy Cinnabon’s as they’re really high in calories (& VERY dense, apparently!)
I was craving one so bad after watching so many videos I actually looked it up online, & back then you COULD order them to your door! It wasn’t cheap though which put me off! I just looked it up again to send you the link & they’ve now closed business here in the U.K. 😩
Thanks for confirming how delicious they are though Ana.. now I’m craving one, probably a good thing they don’t deliver 🤣 xx
